<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Undergrad Abroad Admissions</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/Admission.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/Home.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>

   <!--  Header From -->
   <%- include('partials/header') %> 

    <div class="page-container">
        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <section class="hero-section">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <h1>Undergrad Abroad</h1>
                <div class="breadcrumb">
                    <a href="#">Home</a>
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i>
                    <a href="#">Admissions</a>
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i>
                    <span>Undergrad Abroad</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Main Content Section -->
        <div class="main-content">
            <div class="content-wrapper">
                <!-- Left Side Content -->
                <div class="content-left">
                    <div class="intro-text">
                        <p class="highlight-text">
                            Doing your undergraduate in abroadâ€‹ opens doors to multiple opportunities and a globally recognized degree. Popular destinations like the USA, UK, Canada, Australia, Germany, etc., offer cutting-edge technology, facilities, innovative teaching methods, and diverse cultural experiences.
                        </p>
                        
                        <p>
                            The urge to study undergraduate courses abroad is not only because of the quality of education provided but also because of the career prospects it unlocks. According to recent data, over 1.3 million students are enrolled in global universities abroad in 2024 under multiple courses like business, STEM, health sciences, etc.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Overview Table -->
                    <div class="overview-section">
                        <h2>Overview Table</h2>
                        <div class="table-container">
                            <table class="overview-table">
                                <tbody>
                                    <tr>
                                        <th>Aspects of Studying Undergraduate in Abroad</th>
                                        <td>Details</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <!-- Add Education -->
                                    <tr>
                                        <th>Eligibility</th>
                                        <td>Completion of 12th with a minimum percentage from 60% to 80% and English proficiency tests like IELTS (6.0-7.5) or TOEFL (80-100).</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <th>Popular Undergrad Exams</th>
                                        <td>SAT, ACT (US mostly), IELTS, TOEFL, and PTE</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <!-- Add more rows as per your data -->
                                </tbody>
                            </table>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Reasons Section -->
                    <div class="reasons-section">
                        <h2>Reasons to Study Undergraduate Abroad</h2>
                        <div class="reasons-grid">
                            <div class="reason-card">
                                <i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i>
                                <h3>World Class Education</h3>
                                <p>Experience a diverse choice of subject combinations, flexible curriculum, state-of-the-art infrastructure, research resources, and world-class faculties.</p>
                            </div>
                            <!-- Add more reason cards -->
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Right Side Form -->
                <div class="content-right">
                    <div class="enquiry-form-container">
                        <div class="form-header">
                            <h3>Planning to study abroad?</h3>
                            <p>Get free 1-on-1 counselling with our experts</p>
                        </div>
                        <form id="enquiryForm" class="enquiry-form" action="/Undergrad_AbroadForm" method="POST">
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <input type="text" id="firstName" name="firstName" required>
                                <label for="firstName">First Name</label>
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <input type="text" id="lastName" name="lastName" required>
                                <label for="lastName">Last Name</label>
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
                                <label for="email">Email ID</label>
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <input type="tel" id="mobile" name="mobile" required>
                                <label for="mobile">Mobile Number</label>
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <select id="program" name="program" required>
                                    <option value="">Select Program</option>
                                    <option value="">Adminstion Consulting</option>
                                    <option value="CMAT">CMAT</option>
                                    <option value="SAT">SAT</option>
                                    <option value="PSAT">PSAT</option>
                                    <option value="ACT">ACT</option>
                                    <option value="IELTS">IELTS</option>
                                    <option value="PTE">PTE</option>
                                    <option value="TOEFL">TOEFL</option>
                                    <option value="Academic Tutoring">Academic Tutoring</option>
                                </select>
                            </div>
                    
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <select id="city" name="city" required>
                                    <option value="">Select City</option>
                                    <option value="Mumbai">Mumbai</option>
                                    <option value="Mumbai">Mumbai</option>
                                    <option value="Mumbai">Mumbai</option>
                                    <option value="Mumbai">Mumbai</option>
                                    <option value="Mumbai">Mumbai</option>
                                    <!-- Add more options -->
                                </select>
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group checkbox">
                                <input type="checkbox" id="authorize" name="authorize" required>
                                <label for="authorize">
                                    I authorize Manya - The Princeton Review to contact me even if my number is registered with DND.
                                </label>
                            </div>
                            <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">Submit</button>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <%- include('partials/footer')%>
    </div>

    <script src="../js/Home.js"></script>
    <script src="../js/Admisstion.js"></script>
</body>
</html>